The paper proposes a generative model for EEG analysis using kernel assumptions and variational inference. This suggests that the paper could fall under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
